Package: proven
Title: Safe, Validated Operations Library for R
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R:
    person("Hyperpolymath", email = "hyperpolymath@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides 38 type-safe modules with overflow checking, XSS prevention,
    path traversal protection, email/URL/phone validation, IP classification,
    cryptographic operations, data structures (buffer, queue, bloom filter, LRU cache,
    graph), resilience patterns (rate limiter, circuit breaker, retry, monotonic),
    state machines, calculators, geographic operations, probability, checksums,
    tensors, ML utilities, and HTTP components (header, cookie, content-type).
